  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416450/extras/f966f4706f38836ba090b71c5a57bfdc.avif?t=1740167873\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416450/extras_big/f966f4706f38836ba090b71c5a57bfdc.avif?t=1740167873 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >IT’S YOUR BIRTHDAY!!! and nobody came to celebrate with you… Hell of a Birthday is a First-Person comedic horror game where you play as the Birthday Boy trying to survive your special day. Weird stuff starts happening around the house and you begin to realize that maybe it really was better off being alone on your birthday. From the maker of Bite Night and Invasion of the Halloween Fiends comes another unique adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416450/extras/1333fb76afc0ffe820e99c31c570d756.avif?t=1740167873\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416450/extras_big/1333fb76afc0ffe820e99c31c570d756.avif?t=1740167873 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First Person</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blend of Horror Comedy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro Graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Approx: 45 min - 1 Hour Playing Time</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416450/extras/de61a000240873f7cc98d607aac43c2e.avif?t=1740167873\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416450/extras_big/de61a000240873f7cc98d607aac43c2e.avif?t=1740167873 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416450/extras/f966f4706f38836ba090b71c5a57bfdc.avif?t=1740167873\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416450/extras_big/f966f4706f38836ba090b71c5a57bfdc.avif?t=1740167873 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >IT’S YOUR BIRTHDAY!!! and nobody came to celebrate with you… Hell of a Birthday is a First-Person comedic horror game where you play as the Birthday Boy trying to survive your special day. Weird stuff starts happening around the house and you begin to realize that maybe it really was better off being alone on your birthday. From the maker of Bite Night and Invasion of the Halloween Fiends comes another unique adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416450/extras/1333fb76afc0ffe820e99c31c570d756.avif?t=1740167873\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416450/extras_big/1333fb76afc0ffe820e99c31c570d756.avif?t=1740167873 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First Person</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blend of Horror Comedy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro Graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Approx: 45 min - 1 Hour Playing Time</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416450/extras/de61a000240873f7cc98d607aac43c2e.avif?t=1740167873\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416450/extras_big/de61a000240873f7cc98d607aac43c2e.avif?t=1740167873 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
